Question:- How you can share your docker image without uploading it to docker hub

# Machine on which image is created and copy to another machine
[ec2-user@ip-172-31-40-69 ~]$ sudo su -
[root@ip-172-31-40-69 ~]# yum install docker -y
[root@ip-172-31-40-69 ~]# service docker start
Redirecting to /bin/systemctl start docker.service
